sequenceDiagram
    participant U as 用户
    participant UI as Web UI
    participant API as FastAPI
    participant TM as TaskManager
    participant W as 后台任务线程
    participant CAB as Content Asset Builder
    participant WS as WebSocket Manager

    U->>UI: 创建 search/comments/scripts/merge 任务
    UI->>API: POST /scrape/{task-type}
    API->>TM: create_task(type, params)
    API->>TM: submit(task, worker)
    API-->>UI: task_id + submitted

    TM->>W: 启动后台线程
    W->>TM: status = running
    TM->>WS: broadcast_sync(task_started)
    WS-->>UI: /ws/tasks 状态事件

    alt merge 使用 task-id 构建 Content Asset
        W->>CAB: build_content_asset(search, comments, scripts)
        CAB-->>W: content_asset.csv/jsonl/stats
    else 普通采集任务
        W->>W: 生成任务标准输出
    end

    alt 任务成功
        W->>TM: status = completed + result
        TM->>WS: broadcast_sync(task_completed)
        WS-->>UI: completed + result
        U->>UI: 打开预览或下载
        UI->>API: GET result/preview/export
        API->>TM: get_result_path(task_id)
        TM-->>API: 主结果路径
        API-->>UI: 原始完整结果或旧七字段导出
    else 任务失败
        W->>TM: status = failed + error
        TM->>WS: broadcast_sync(task_failed)
        WS-->>UI: failed + error
    end

    Note over UI,API: 开发环境 Web 为 localhost:15173，API 为 localhost:18080
    Note over API: 发布构建由 api/webui 提供，并挂载在 /ui
